*{{fi}}: [[uudelleenkäynnistää]]
*Spanish: [[reiniciar]]
*Swedish: [[starta om]], [[reboota]]
*Japanese: [[再起動する]] (saikidô suru), [[リブートする]] (ribuuto suru)

===Noun===
'''reboot'''
# an instance of rebooting

